title: Dream Girl
description: Digital art piece created by Katheryn McGuire in April 2025 featuring an original character. A figure sits in the center of the composition in a chair, drawn in green tones. Surrounding her are several figures drawn in pinks and yellows.

title: Birdhouse in Your Soul
description: Digital art piece created by Katheryn McGuire in October 2024 featuring an original character. The title and work reference the song "Birdhouse in Your Soul" by the band They Might Be Giants. A figure, colored in blues and oranges, sits in front of a large birdhouse, haloed by a glowing circle of orange light. The piece is covered with diamond and circle patterns in various colors.

title: Seagulls Cry
description: Digital art piece created by Katheryn McGuire in January 2025 inspired by the visual novel series Umineko: When They Cry by the studio 7th Expansion. A woman is pictured with her back to the camera as she stares down at a smaller figure. A checkboard pattern is applied to multiple parts of the piece in yellow and orange.
